{
  "texts": [
    "The NDT autonomously performs dynamic monitoring of the entire network lifecycle.",
    "This comprehensive surveillance uncovers potential upgrades and enhancements to functionality and performance within the network.",
    "By continuously analyzing real-time data and historical patterns, the NDT can identify opportunities for improvements.",
    "This ensures that the network evolves to meet emerging demands and maintains the optimal performance.",
    "The NDT builds network cognitive capabilities via self-learning and uses adaptive learning methods to infer and implement various network adaptive adjustment strategies to meet different user needs."
  ]
}